  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK414">
<l>kaṟṟila ṉāyiṉuṅ kēṭka vaḵtoruvaṉ</l>
<l>oṟkattuk kūṟṟān tuṇai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although a man be without learning, let him listen (to the teaching of the learned); that will be to him a staff in adversity.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
